title: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', but it changes with settings.
OB: When setting a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com', the title of the hyperlink builder does not remain as 'Hyperlink Options'.
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should remain as 'Hyperlink Options' regardless of the settings.
SR: 1. Open the hyperlink builder. 2. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
